comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) turns in mid-air and makes contact to Dort's (OKC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Dort's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Middleton (MIL) cleanly blocks Williams' (OKC) jump shot attempt before any incidental contact occurs.
Horford (OKC) switches his pivot foot before attempting the shot.
Middleton (MIL) legally contest Horford's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Horford (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Connaughton's (MIL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Portis (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball and any contact with Dort's (OKC) arm is incidental.
Middleton (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bazley's (OKC) path and some contact occurs as they disengage.
Middleton (MIL) receives the pass and takes three steps.  He then lifts his pivot foot.
Dort (OKC) brushes Middleton's (MIL) arm during his driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Portis (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Dort's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Dort (OKC) makes incidental contact to Middleton's (MIL) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
DiVincenzo (MIL) commits a take foul on Horford (OKC).
Dort (OKC) does not establish himself in bounds prior to making contact with the ball.
